<s docid="AP890715-0076" num="36" wdcount="56"> Other ambassadorial nominees rated
as unqualified by the American Academy of Diplomacy include Florida real
estate developer Joseph Zappala, nominated as ambassador to Spain; Melvin L.
Sembler, a real estate executive in Florida named to be ambassador to
Australia; and Della M. Newman, a Seattle, Wash., real estate broker named
to be ambassador to New Zealand.</s>

<s docid="AP890801-0134" num="8" wdcount="28"> Ronald I. Spiers, a veteran U.S.
